oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Grand Ole Opry Duke of Paducah Show at the Ephrata War Memorial Auditorium
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:subject: Grand ole opry (Radio program); Duke of Paducah, 1901-1986
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Three color window card (red and black on yellow) Hatch poster announcing the Duke of Paducah show featuring the George Morgan, Anita Carter, Annie Lou, Danny Dill, Lew Childre and the Candy Kids at the Ephrata war Memorial Field on August 10. Poster features metal photoplates of the Duke of Paducah, George Morgan, Anita Carter, Annie Lou, Danny Dill, and Lew Childre.
